0.woff2" as="font" type="font/woff2" crossorigin="anonymous" data-next-head=""/><link rel="preload" href="/_next/static/media/Boyrun-Regular.woff2" as="font" type="font/woff2" crossorigin="anonymous" data-next-head=""/><link rel="preload" href="https://www.facebook.com/tr?id=792405807634160&amp;ev=PageView&amp;noscript=1" as="image" data-next-head=""/><script type="application/ld+json" data-next-head="">{"@type":"Organization","@context":"https://schema.org","url":"https://www.meetup.com/aws-user-group-madurai/","name":"Meetup","logo":"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/next/images/general/m_redesign_630x630.png","sameAs":["https://www.facebook.com/meetup/","https://twitter.com/Meetup/","https://www.youtube.com/meetup","https://www.instagram.com/meetup/"]}</script><meta name="description" content="he AWS User Group Madurai is a community of technology enthusiasts, professionals, and students who are interested in learning and sharing knowledge about Amazon Web Services (AWS) and cloud computing. The purpose of the group is to create a platform for individuals to connect, network, and collabor" data-next-head=""/><meta property="fb:app_id" content="2403839689" data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:site_name" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:type" content="article" data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:title" content="AWS User Group Madurai | Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:description" content="he AWS User Group Madurai is a community of technology enthusiasts, professionals, and students who are interested in learning and sharing knowledge about Amazon Web Services (AWS) and cloud computing. The purpose of the group is to create a platform for individuals to connect, network, and collabor" data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:url" content="https://www.meetup.com/aws-user-group-madurai/" data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:image" content="https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/c/1/4/8/600_511249480.jpeg" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:android:app_name" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:android:package" content="com.meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:ios:app_store_id" content="375990038" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:ios:app_name" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:web:should_fallback" content="true" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:android:url" content="meetup://" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:ios:url" content="meetup://" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:web:url" content="https://www.meetup.com/" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:site" content="@meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:image" content="https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/c/1/4/8/600_511249480.jpeg" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:description" content="he AWS User Group Madurai is a community of technology enthusiasts, professionals, and students who are interested in learning and sharing knowledge about Amazon Web Services (AWS) and cloud computing. The purpose of the group is to create a platform for individuals to connect, network, and collabor" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:id:iphone" content="375990038" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:name:iphone" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:id:ipad" content="375990038" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:name:ipad" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:id:googleplay" content="com.meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:name:googleplay" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta name="robots" content="index, follow, max-image-preview:large" data-next-head=""/><script type="application/ld+json" data-next-head="">[{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Event","name":"Claude & OpenClaw on AWS","url":"https://www.meetup.com/aws-user-group-madurai/events/315340105/","description":"# 🚀 Builders Skill Sprint: OpenClaw Month\n\n## Claude & OpenClaw on AWS\n\nJoin AWS User Group Madurai for a special **Builders Skill Sprint** dedicated to **OpenClaw Month**, where we'll explore how to build production-grade AI agents using **Claude, OpenClaw, and AWS**.\nThis session is designed for builders who want to move beyond AI demos and learn how to create scalable, autonomous agent systems that can solve real-world problems.\n\n### What You'll Learn\n\n🔹 Introduction to OpenClaw and the Agentic AI ecosystem\n🔹 Leveraging Claude for reasoning, planning, and decision-making\n🔹 Building AI agents on AWS infrastructure\n🔹 Agent orchestration, tool calling, and workflow automation\n🔹 Deploying production-ready agent applications\n🔹 Best practices for security, monitoring, and scaling\n\n### Builders Skill Sprint Highlights\n\n✅ Hands-on learning experience\n✅ Live demos and architecture walkthroughs\n✅ Open-source AI agent development practices\n✅ Real-world use cases and implementation strategies\n✅ Community networking with AWS and AI builders\n\n### Who Should Attend?\n\n* Developers and Software Engineers\n* Cloud & DevOps Professionals\n* AI/ML Enthusiasts\n* Solution Architects\n* Students and Emerging Builders","startDate":"2026-06-28T04:30:00.000Z","endDate":"2026-06-28T06:30:00.000Z","eventStatus":"https://schema.org/EventScheduled","image":"","eventAttendanceMode":"https://schema.org/OnlineEventAttendanceMode","location":{"@type":"VirtualLocation","url":"https://www.meetup.com/aws-user-group-madurai/events/315340105/"},"organizer":{"@type":"Organization","name":"AWS User Group Madurai","url":"https://www.meetup.com/aws-user-group-madurai/"},"performer":"AWS User Group Madurai"}]</script><script type="application/ld+json" data-next-head="">{"@type":"Organization","@context":"https://schema.org","url":"https://www.meetup.com/aws-user-group-madurai/","name":"AWS User Group Madurai","image":"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/c/1/4/8/600_511249480.webp","foundingDate":"2023-03-11T20:26:39.000Z","address":{"location":{"@type":"Place","address":{"@type":"PostalAddress","addressLocality":"Madurai","addressRegion":"","addressCountry":"in"}}},"sameAs":["https://twitter.com/awsugmdu","https://instagram.com/awsugmdu"]}</script><script type="application/ld+json" data-next-head="">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"BreadcrumbList","itemListElement":[{"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"item":{"@id":"https://www.meetup.com/aws-user-group-madurai/","name":"AWS User Group Madurai"}}]}</script><meta property="geo.position" content="9.92;78.12" data-next-head=""/><meta property="geo.placename" content="Madurai" data-next-head=""/><meta property="geo.region" content="in" data-next-head=""/><link rel="canonical" href="https://www.meetup.com/aws-user-group-madurai/" data-next-head=""/><link rel="preconnect" href="https://secure.meetupstatic.com" data-next-head=""/><link rel="dns-prefetch" href="https://secure.meetupstatic.com" data-next-head=""/><link rel="preconnect" href="https://secure-content.meetupstatic.com" data-next-head=""/><link rel="dns-prefetch" href="https://secure-content.meetupstatic.com" data-next-head=""/><link rel="preconnect" href="https://www.googletagmanager.com" data-next-head=""/><link rel="dns-prefetch" href="https://www.googletagmanager.com" data-next-head=""/><title data-next-head="">AWS User Group Madurai | Meetup</title><link rel="preload" href="https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/c/1/4/8/clean_511249480.webp" as="image" data-next-head=""/><link rel="preload" href="https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/b/7/9/7/highres_534826999.jpeg" as="image" data-next-head=""/><link rel="preload" href="https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/3/3/f/6/highres_534613302.jpeg" as="image" data-next-head=""/><link rel="preload" href="https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/d/f/5/3/highres_534537171.jpeg" as="image" data-next-head=""/><meta name="next_csrf" content="5a6773